        such as <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">mice</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">rats</ENAMEX>, rabbits or <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">pigs</ENAMEX> do not develop typical
        <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">renal disease</ENAMEX> when given either <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Stx</ENAMEX> or 
        <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">E. coli</ENAMEX> <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">0157</TIMEX>:<NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">H7</NUMEX> [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">14</TIMEX> ] . Further,
        animal models that most closely reflect human <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">HUS</ENAMEX> are only
