        an effect of sex <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">steroids</ENAMEX> on renal cell Stx-1
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">responsiveness</ENAMEX>; such <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">systems</ENAMEX> have clearly been demonstrated
        to be responsive to sex <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">steroids</ENAMEX> (e.g.
